eZp Collective Reports Admin README

What is the eZp Collective Reports Admin extension?
================================

eZp Collective Reports Admin is a true eZ Publish extension
that provides a simple semi-dynamic module view which displays
information and links to individual report views available with the system.

eZp Collective Reports Admin version
=======================

The current version of eZp Collective Reports Admin is 0.1.0
Last Major update: April 9, 2015


